title: Hawk and Dove Vol.1989 #22 - mysteriously missing from MTCDC
description:
If you downloaded the hawk and dove torrents floating around last year you would have noticed that issue #22 of the third series was missing

 So I broke down and picked up a copy and scanned it with my own two little hands.

 So for all you completest and anal-rententives out there here you go and please leave me some props so that I know my work does not go unnoticed.

 Enjoy and Seed
